WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: zh-CN

00:00.000 --> 00:02.000
MkvDrama.Org

01:35.280 --> 01:37.640
Episode 12

01:40.720 --> 01:43.560
Is that Mistress Zhong in the carriage ahead?

01:49.120 --> 01:50.160
Hold up.

01:52.920 --> 01:55.560
Junior Lord Wu, what can I do for you?

01:56.120 --> 01:58.600
Mistress, you are such a busy woman.

01:58.680 --> 02:00.120
I have sent you invitations several times

02:01.120 --> 02:02.440
but you've never responded.

02:03.720 --> 02:04.960
You must be joking.

02:05.320 --> 02:06.760
I am a married woman.

02:06.840 --> 02:09.280
It's inappropriate for me to meet you.

02:09.360 --> 02:10.560
You can go directly to my husband

02:10.640 --> 02:11.960
if you're in need.

02:17.280 --> 02:19.520
You and I have something to talk about.

02:19.960 --> 02:24.080
Like that maid in Zhong Residence.

02:24.560 --> 02:26.320
I don't understand.

02:26.400 --> 02:27.640
Which maid?

02:28.680 --> 02:29.680
Mu Yao.

02:31.200 --> 02:32.920
So you are talking about her.

02:33.280 --> 02:34.640
In fact

02:34.720 --> 02:37.440
she will become my husband's concubine

02:37.720 --> 02:38.880
next month.

02:48.160 --> 02:50.600
You're such a forgiving woman.

02:51.520 --> 02:54.520
What, you changed your attitude

02:54.600 --> 02:55.720
just because I won't cooperate with you?

02:56.120 --> 02:57.440
How did you know

02:57.760 --> 02:59.000
what I was going to do?

02:59.560 --> 03:02.160
Rather than wasting time and energy on me

03:02.240 --> 03:04.480
divert your attention to someone else.

03:04.560 --> 03:07.280
After all, the ball is in her court.

03:07.880 --> 03:09.760
If she really cared about you

03:09.840 --> 03:12.480
would you have to solve the issue alone?

03:13.320 --> 03:15.760
Sometimes a step too late

03:15.840 --> 03:17.000
and you may never catch up.

03:18.800 --> 03:19.840
What do you know?

03:23.680 --> 03:25.760
You asked for Mu Yao

03:25.840 --> 03:27.440
at the incense banquet, didn't you?

03:27.720 --> 03:29.560
If you really care about her

03:29.640 --> 03:31.600
you should ask her what she thinks of you.

03:31.680 --> 03:33.600
Otherwise, no matter how hard you work

03:33.680 --> 03:34.800
it will be in vain.

03:36.640 --> 03:37.640
What makes you say

03:37.720 --> 03:38.800
that my efforts would be in vain?

03:40.840 --> 03:45.600
You and Mu Yao only met a few times

03:45.880 --> 03:48.480
and she doesn't like you.

03:48.560 --> 03:51.480
Why are you so obsessed with her?

03:51.560 --> 03:53.520
Sometimes, despite what already happened

03:53.600 --> 03:56.000
it's up to us to alter the outcome.

03:56.320 --> 03:58.800
You don't have to follow the established path.

04:09.280 --> 04:11.800
Junior Lord Wu, think about what I said.

04:11.880 --> 04:14.040
If you are still in the city next month

04:14.120 --> 04:15.160
you are welcome

04:15.240 --> 04:16.800
to attend their wedding banquet.

04:16.880 --> 04:18.840
I will take my leave.

04:21.080 --> 04:22.080
Let's go.

04:34.720 --> 04:36.080
Does the Junior Lord of the Wu Family

04:36.160 --> 04:37.520
really like Mu Yao?

04:38.280 --> 04:39.320
I guess so.

04:39.760 --> 04:41.080
Otherwise, why is he still thinking about her

04:41.160 --> 04:42.160
after so many years?

04:42.680 --> 04:44.400
Childhood crushes

04:44.480 --> 04:45.920
are the most unforgettable after all.

04:46.600 --> 04:47.720
So many years?

04:47.800 --> 04:49.120
Did they know each other before?

04:53.120 --> 04:54.840
Master...

04:55.640 --> 04:56.760
Master...

04:56.840 --> 04:58.800
Zhong's Garden is amazing.

04:59.320 --> 05:00.320
Even a bird here

05:00.400 --> 05:01.800
can speak like a human being.

05:02.200 --> 05:03.200
Get down here.

05:04.520 --> 05:05.640
Get down here.

05:08.440 --> 05:10.760
He had told me about his plan

05:10.840 --> 05:12.640
because he wanted to work with me.

05:13.480 --> 05:16.400
This parrot offended four people.

05:17.120 --> 05:18.920
What an annoying pet.

05:19.440 --> 05:22.640
Why don't you let him take away Mu Yao?

05:22.880 --> 05:24.160
He can't take her away.

05:24.240 --> 05:25.560
That's the destined outcome for him.

05:27.160 --> 05:29.280
I told him that

05:29.360 --> 05:31.680
because I wanted him to accept this reality

05:31.760 --> 05:33.240
and stop making himself a fool

05:33.320 --> 05:36.000
while embroiled in their stories.

05:48.440 --> 05:49.640
Why have you come to me all of a sudden?

05:49.720 --> 05:51.480
Did you find out something again?

06:33.760 --> 06:35.880
This is a gift for Concubine Mu

06:35.960 --> 06:37.360
from Her Highness.

06:45.600 --> 06:47.800
Congratulations, Master.

06:53.480 --> 06:54.600
Concubine Mu?

07:04.480 --> 07:06.080
Thank you, Steward Gao.

07:09.800 --> 07:11.200
I have delivered both the gift and order

07:11.280 --> 07:12.720
from Her Highness.

07:12.800 --> 07:14.520
I'll take my leave.

07:14.600 --> 07:15.720
Thank you, Steward Gao.

07:25.600 --> 07:27.760
You went to Zhong's Garden yesterday

07:27.840 --> 07:29.120
and today Her Highness wants me

07:29.200 --> 07:30.480
take Mu Yao as a concubine.

07:31.080 --> 07:32.560
What are you trying to do?

07:32.640 --> 07:34.560
I just did what you wanted to do.

07:35.120 --> 07:36.600
Why are you still not satisfied?

07:38.200 --> 07:39.640
Do you know what you are doing?

07:40.080 --> 07:41.680
Didn't you proclaim that

07:41.760 --> 07:43.280
that Mu Yao was your woman?

07:43.560 --> 07:45.080
I gave you what you wanted.

07:45.680 --> 07:47.120
Why are you getting angry at me?

07:47.200 --> 07:48.320
Since when did you start

07:48.400 --> 07:49.560
sparing a thought for me?

07:53.840 --> 07:55.040
Are you thinking

07:55.440 --> 07:56.920
the position of the concubine

07:57.000 --> 07:58.000
is not good enough for her?

07:58.720 --> 08:02.480
Why don't you let her take my place?

08:03.080 --> 08:05.000
Didn't you say that I was a giving person?

08:05.080 --> 08:07.240
I can step aside. I don't mind.

08:13.560 --> 08:15.920
I know what you want to do.

08:27.480 --> 08:28.840
Are you really the one behind this?

08:29.560 --> 08:31.640
Who else could it be?

08:31.720 --> 08:34.080
Do you think that if I'm a concubine

08:34.160 --> 08:35.880
you will be able to control me?

08:36.440 --> 08:39.080
Mu Yao, you have always been smart

08:39.160 --> 08:40.680
but why have you become dense now?

08:41.520 --> 08:43.320
Which would be an easy target for bullies?

08:43.400 --> 08:44.720
A maid or a concubine?

08:46.240 --> 08:47.400
So, you want to humiliate me

08:47.480 --> 08:48.640
by making me a concubine?

08:49.200 --> 08:50.440
Think whatever you want.

08:50.520 --> 08:51.800
I know you don't believe me

08:52.280 --> 08:53.320
but now I really have no intention

08:53.400 --> 08:54.680
of competing with you.

08:54.760 --> 08:56.400
Otherwise, I wouldn't give in, would I?

08:56.800 --> 08:58.320
You can be wary of me.

08:58.400 --> 08:59.520
I don't care.

08:59.600 --> 09:02.240
Anyway, you'll come to know I don't mean ill.

09:25.560 --> 09:28.320
Sir, where are you going?

09:28.400 --> 09:29.680
???Let's leave first.                    ???Sir.

09:30.800 --> 09:32.920
You can run but you can't hide.

09:33.000 --> 09:34.320
Word got out.

09:34.400 --> 09:35.520
What should I do?

09:36.000 --> 09:37.040
What should I do?

09:39.560 --> 09:41.440
Tell me! What do I do?

09:44.640 --> 09:45.840
My sister is smart.

09:46.200 --> 09:47.280
She will find a way.

09:47.440 --> 09:48.720
Come on. Let's go.

10:03.400 --> 10:04.640
No wedding ceremonies for concubines?

10:04.720 --> 10:05.880
What's the reason for that?

10:06.360 --> 10:08.560
It's a rule passed down from the ancestors.

10:08.840 --> 10:11.720
Then can she wear the wedding dress?

10:12.080 --> 10:13.600
A concubine

10:13.680 --> 10:15.920
can only wear a pink wedding dress.

10:18.400 --> 10:19.600
Is there an exception?

10:19.680 --> 10:20.680
No!

10:20.920 --> 10:22.040
On top of that

10:22.120 --> 10:25.080
concubines can only enter through the side door

10:25.160 --> 10:28.280
and they have to offer tea to the mistress

10:28.360 --> 10:29.560
before the whole process is over.

10:30.520 --> 10:32.760
I didn't know there were so many rules.

10:32.840 --> 10:35.360
You're from a reputable family

10:35.720 --> 10:38.040
and Butler Hua has never taken a concubine

10:38.120 --> 10:39.640
so it makes sense that you don't know.

10:40.160 --> 10:41.680
We can't go against the rules

10:41.760 --> 10:42.880
to preserve the honour

10:42.960 --> 10:44.440
of a rich and powerful family.

10:45.640 --> 10:47.880
Do you have any other questions, Mistress?

10:48.560 --> 10:49.560
Well...

10:50.120 --> 10:51.440
A wedding banquet is fine, no?

10:52.880 --> 10:54.080
A wedding banquet?

10:54.440 --> 10:55.440
Yes.

11:00.480 --> 11:02.000
It's your choice, Mistress.

11:02.800 --> 11:05.760
Who organised my wedding banquet?

11:07.080 --> 11:08.080
Butler Ji.

11:09.280 --> 11:11.640
Tell him to duplicate what he had done before

11:12.520 --> 11:13.840
and invite the same group of guests.

11:14.120 --> 11:15.160
What?

11:15.240 --> 11:19.440
And drop the ritual of serving tea.

11:20.160 --> 11:21.160
This is...

11:27.120 --> 11:28.120
All right.

11:37.760 --> 11:39.800
She didn't argue with me today.

11:40.400 --> 11:43.200
Mistress, you've been so enthusiastic.

11:43.280 --> 11:44.280
People who don't know might think

11:44.360 --> 11:45.440
you're the one getting married.

11:45.520 --> 11:46.800
Housemaid Li has trained herself

11:46.880 --> 11:48.160
to be unflustered under stress

11:48.240 --> 11:49.440
or else you would be the death of her.

11:52.840 --> 11:54.720
Mistress, I'll get back to work.

12:09.360 --> 12:11.520
You blind servant! Didn't you see me?

12:11.600 --> 12:12.600
???I'll kill you.                        ???Sir.

12:12.680 --> 12:13.840
???We're in Zhong Residence.       ???This is...

12:14.120 --> 12:15.400
Young Master Hua, are you all right?

12:16.600 --> 12:17.880
My hands were tired

12:17.960 --> 12:19.920
and I didn't notice you coming in this way.

12:21.360 --> 12:23.440
It's you. I...

12:23.720 --> 12:26.920
Sir, she'll be Master's concubine soon.

12:27.800 --> 12:29.520
The news spread so quickly.

12:29.600 --> 12:30.800
But I haven't served tea

12:30.880 --> 12:32.640
so I'm still a maid.

12:32.720 --> 12:35.400
Young Master Hua, why are you in such a hurry?

12:35.920 --> 12:37.480
I'm here to see my sister.

12:37.920 --> 12:39.640
Mistress has not gone out today

12:39.720 --> 12:41.480
so she should be in her compound.

12:41.560 --> 12:43.280
Do you need me to lead the way?

12:43.640 --> 12:45.080
That'd be nice. Let's go.

12:45.160 --> 12:47.520
We won't trouble you. I know the way.

12:47.600 --> 12:49.040
Sir, let's go.

12:52.760 --> 12:54.240
Sir, we should go.

12:54.320 --> 12:55.320
Stay focused.

12:55.400 --> 12:57.000
Don't forget what we are here for today.

12:57.440 --> 12:58.480
Right...

13:03.640 --> 13:07.280
Mistress, here's the guest list.

13:07.760 --> 13:09.160
Thank you, Butler Ji.

13:09.240 --> 13:10.240
Send the invitation cards

13:10.320 --> 13:11.360
to everyone on the list.

13:11.840 --> 13:12.840
Yes, Mistress.

13:15.360 --> 13:18.320
Mistress, if there's anything else

13:18.400 --> 13:19.760
just ask for me any time.

13:20.760 --> 13:23.080
I'm leaving to make preparations.

13:30.480 --> 13:31.720
Have you gotten enough sleep?

13:42.760 --> 13:43.920
I didn't sleep.

13:44.440 --> 13:46.440
I was just distracted.

13:49.680 --> 13:51.480
Are you preparing

13:51.560 --> 13:52.760
for the wedding banquet next month?

13:53.400 --> 13:55.200
She's just a concubine.

13:55.280 --> 13:56.960
I don't think it's necessary for you

13:57.040 --> 13:58.080
to do so much.

13:58.480 --> 13:59.800
When I came here this morning

13:59.880 --> 14:01.120
I ran into that maid

14:01.200 --> 14:03.800
but didn't recognise her until I talked to her.

14:04.320 --> 14:06.400
Isn't she the one I saw

14:06.480 --> 14:08.760
coming out of Master's study?

14:09.480 --> 14:12.240
I told you, but you didn't listen.

14:12.720 --> 14:13.760
Look what happened.

14:13.840 --> 14:15.040
She got what she wanted

14:16.240 --> 14:17.240
and made you work so hard

14:17.320 --> 14:19.880
to prepare for the wedding banquet.

14:19.960 --> 14:22.040
Why don't you just pretend to be sick

14:22.120 --> 14:23.120
and let someone else take over?

14:23.200 --> 14:26.680
Let my brother-in-law handle this hard task

14:26.760 --> 14:29.040
and he'll know the difficulty you're facing.

14:29.400 --> 14:30.840
You're in trouble again?

14:34.560 --> 14:35.560
No.

14:36.680 --> 14:38.000
No!

14:38.280 --> 14:40.760
I missed you so I came to see you.

14:41.080 --> 14:42.400
If everything was fine

14:42.480 --> 14:43.520
you wouldn't be speaking and acting

14:43.600 --> 14:44.960
like a normal person.

14:48.320 --> 14:49.320
Tell me.

14:49.400 --> 14:50.400
What did you do

14:50.480 --> 14:51.480
to make our father angry again?

14:55.920 --> 14:58.120
You're so smart.

14:58.200 --> 15:00.000
I can't hide anything from you.

15:00.800 --> 15:03.440
It's not a big deal.

15:03.520 --> 15:06.560
I gave someone one of my concubines.

15:08.440 --> 15:09.640
And?

15:10.080 --> 15:12.840
Yes, it's not a big deal at all.

15:18.480 --> 15:20.000
The banquet preparation has worn me out

15:20.080 --> 15:21.360
these few days.

15:21.440 --> 15:23.680
Just get to the point, why don't you?

15:23.760 --> 15:24.760
If all that you did was

15:24.840 --> 15:25.840
give a concubine to someone

15:25.920 --> 15:27.400
you wouldn't need to come to me.

15:29.240 --> 15:31.040
It's just about a woman, really.

15:32.160 --> 15:34.200
Fine. Since you don't have anything to say

15:34.280 --> 15:35.320
you may go back now.

15:35.400 --> 15:37.600
I'm busy. I don't have time for you.

15:38.880 --> 15:41.400
Fine. I'll tell you the truth.

15:41.480 --> 15:43.160
But could you put in a good word for me

15:43.240 --> 15:44.720
in front of our parents?

15:44.800 --> 15:47.320
They always listen to you.

15:48.680 --> 15:49.680
Tell me

15:49.760 --> 15:51.040
and I'll decide if I want to do that for you.

15:55.440 --> 15:56.640
I'm telling you

15:56.720 --> 15:58.920
everything in our house

15:59.200 --> 16:00.760
is of high quality.

16:00.840 --> 16:01.840
You don't like her? It's all right.

16:02.240 --> 16:03.560
There will be more.

16:03.640 --> 16:05.360
There are better ones.

16:06.560 --> 16:08.000
Come on. Let's drink.

16:09.400 --> 16:10.760
Bottoms up.

16:12.440 --> 16:14.320
B-B-Beauty, don't go.

16:16.120 --> 16:17.200
Who are you calling "beauty"?

16:19.440 --> 16:20.760
I thought

16:20.840 --> 16:24.760
there were plenty of beautiful women here.

16:24.840 --> 16:26.000
Aren't there?

16:26.080 --> 16:28.280
But I only just saw a woman

16:28.360 --> 16:30.320
who was slightly above average.

16:30.400 --> 16:31.640
And you know what?

16:31.720 --> 16:33.320
She ran away.

16:33.840 --> 16:35.800
No problem.

16:36.400 --> 16:38.280
If you want her

16:38.360 --> 16:40.600
just take her away later.

16:42.440 --> 16:46.440
Sir, that is the 19th concubine you just took.

16:46.800 --> 16:47.800
Which one?

16:49.160 --> 16:50.480
The one whom you bought

16:50.560 --> 16:51.880
and was your maid at first.

16:54.480 --> 16:57.240
What are you talking about? My concubine?

16:57.720 --> 17:00.920
She is merely a maid I bought.

17:01.520 --> 17:04.840
Since Brother Wang likes her

17:04.920 --> 17:06.760
just take her with her.

17:06.840 --> 17:08.720
Thank you very much, Brother Hua.

17:08.800 --> 17:11.680
You're indeed the son of the Hua family

17:11.760 --> 17:13.760
and your generosity amazes me.

17:14.840 --> 17:16.000
Why are you still here?

17:16.280 --> 17:17.480
Bring her here.

17:17.800 --> 17:18.800
Well...

17:21.200 --> 17:22.840
???You...                       ???I'll do it...

17:28.440 --> 17:30.120
Come on. Let's drink.

17:33.320 --> 17:34.640
Why hasn't she come yet?

17:34.720 --> 17:36.120
I can't wait.

17:36.200 --> 17:37.640
My compound is big

17:37.720 --> 17:39.080
so it would take her some time to come here.

17:39.160 --> 17:40.880
???How rich...       ???Just wait a little more.

17:46.200 --> 17:47.200
Where is she?

17:49.280 --> 17:50.400
Speak.

17:57.320 --> 17:58.680
How dare she!

17:58.760 --> 17:59.960
I'm going to fix her.

18:01.560 --> 18:03.720
???Sir!                     ???I'll go with you.

18:04.360 --> 18:05.520
Tell me, Qian.

18:05.840 --> 18:07.720
My friend wanted a woman in my compound.

18:07.800 --> 18:08.880
How could I say no?

18:09.200 --> 18:12.280
But that maid... was ungrateful.

18:12.360 --> 18:13.600
The moment I got distracted

18:13.680 --> 18:15.280
she hit her head against a pillar and died.

18:15.360 --> 18:18.720
She brought bad luck to my compound.

18:19.640 --> 18:21.960
In fact, I had everything taken care of

18:22.040 --> 18:24.640
but some lowly maid leaked the incident

18:25.800 --> 18:27.560
so I'm afraid to go home now.

18:28.360 --> 18:31.800
What do you want me to do?

18:32.160 --> 18:33.240
I suppose our father

18:33.320 --> 18:34.400
would have found out about this by now

18:34.480 --> 18:37.280
and he will punish me for this.

18:37.760 --> 18:41.160
Could you put in a good word for me

18:41.240 --> 18:42.360
in front of him?

18:43.160 --> 18:46.000
So you don't think you should be punished?

18:46.080 --> 18:47.160
Of course.

18:47.880 --> 18:49.920
Be punished because of a maid?

18:50.240 --> 18:51.680
How embarrassed would I be if word got out?

18:51.760 --> 18:52.760
Qian, you have no idea.

18:52.840 --> 18:56.440
That maid was once convicted and sold.

18:56.800 --> 18:59.720
I shouldn't have bought her

18:59.800 --> 19:01.680
out of sympathy.

19:02.720 --> 19:06.440
Sure enough, people like her deserve it

19:06.520 --> 19:07.680
and they can't be good.

19:08.200 --> 19:10.280
You think people like her deserve it?

19:10.360 --> 19:11.760
Yes. See what she got me into?

19:11.840 --> 19:12.840
Get out!

19:13.240 --> 19:14.240
Qian.

19:14.440 --> 19:17.760
I've been nicer to you recently

19:17.840 --> 19:18.920
so you think I'm going to

19:19.000 --> 19:20.120
take care of this for you?

19:20.480 --> 19:21.480
I...

19:21.560 --> 19:23.240
I never meddle in your private affairs.

19:23.320 --> 19:24.480
I thought...

19:24.560 --> 19:26.720
I thought at least those women in your compound

19:26.800 --> 19:29.280
were social climbers and willing parties.

19:29.840 --> 19:31.560
It turned out I was wrong.

19:32.280 --> 19:35.360
You've become so reckless and brazen!

19:35.440 --> 19:36.560
Hua Rongzhou, come in.

19:45.720 --> 19:48.680
Hua Rongzhou, take my brother

19:48.760 --> 19:49.760
back to Hua Residence.

19:56.760 --> 19:57.760
Forget it.

19:59.840 --> 20:01.320
Go get Nanfeng here for me.

20:02.600 --> 20:03.640
Yes, Mistress.

20:20.720 --> 20:21.840
Mistress.

20:23.120 --> 20:24.200
Nanfeng.

20:24.280 --> 20:26.120
I want you to do something for me

20:26.200 --> 20:28.040
and I'll owe you one.

20:28.560 --> 20:29.800
Mistress, don't put it like that.

20:30.440 --> 20:31.840
I work for you.

20:31.920 --> 20:33.280
Just tell me whatever you want me to do.

20:33.840 --> 20:35.760
Go to Hua Residence with some men.

20:36.120 --> 20:37.560
Tell them it's my instruction.

20:37.640 --> 20:40.360
Ask the women in my brother's compound

20:40.440 --> 20:41.840
if any of them want to leave.

20:42.320 --> 20:43.760
Those who wish to leave

20:43.840 --> 20:45.040
bring them here.

20:45.640 --> 20:46.760
I'll give them enough money

20:46.840 --> 20:49.080
to live comfortably for the rest of their lives.

20:49.880 --> 20:51.160
You are Master's guard

20:51.240 --> 20:53.600
so my father would probably not stop you.

20:53.680 --> 20:55.520
W-W-Wait.

20:55.600 --> 20:56.680
What are you going to do?

20:57.040 --> 20:58.920
You don't think you've done anything wrong?

20:59.480 --> 21:04.680
Does the life of a maid mean nothing to you?

21:05.720 --> 21:07.160
She's just a slave.

21:07.240 --> 21:10.320
I bought her so her life belonged to me.

21:10.400 --> 21:12.320
She wanted to kill herself.

21:12.400 --> 21:13.920
What could I do about it?

21:16.320 --> 21:17.640
She's just a slave?

21:18.640 --> 21:19.760
Isn't a slave a human?

21:20.760 --> 21:22.400
Don't slaves have loved ones?

21:23.440 --> 21:26.480
What if this happens to me?

21:27.560 --> 21:28.720
What if I became a slave?

21:29.320 --> 21:32.560
What if I were exiled or sold?

21:33.320 --> 21:34.680
Will you say that

21:35.600 --> 21:37.800
I deserve it as well?

21:38.560 --> 21:39.800
Put yourself in her shoes.

21:40.360 --> 21:44.120
Imagine how painful it is for her family.

21:44.200 --> 21:47.200
That maid was once a criminal.

21:47.280 --> 21:48.560
She was an orphan

21:48.640 --> 21:49.760
and had no family.

21:49.840 --> 21:50.920
That is why you think

21:51.000 --> 21:52.440
you've done nothing wrong?

22:05.160 --> 22:07.000
Nanfeng, I'll be counting on you.

22:07.520 --> 22:09.000
Please take my brother back

22:09.400 --> 22:10.680
and tell my father

22:10.760 --> 22:14.320
that if he still won't discipline his son

22:14.880 --> 22:16.760
I'll do it for him.

22:21.840 --> 22:23.200
???Yes, Mistress.          ???You should be glad

22:23.280 --> 22:24.600
that you are my brother.

22:24.680 --> 22:28.040
Otherwise, you wouldn't stand here intact now.

22:33.520 --> 22:34.600
Do I need to make you walk

22:34.680 --> 22:35.760
Young Master Hua?

22:58.880 --> 23:01.960
Has the bergamot incense gone bad?

23:03.280 --> 23:06.960
Why is there a strange fragrance?

23:12.760 --> 23:13.760
I don't think so.

23:17.880 --> 23:19.040
Put that away.

23:30.440 --> 23:31.880
This is the request of Mistress.

23:32.200 --> 23:33.560
Please approve, Butler Hua.

23:34.800 --> 23:35.880
Huang.

23:36.680 --> 23:39.600
Take him to Hua Shen's compound.

23:40.360 --> 23:41.400
Yes, Sir.

23:42.160 --> 23:43.160
This way, please.

23:59.400 --> 24:00.520
My dear.

24:09.280 --> 24:11.600
He merely bought a maid.

24:11.680 --> 24:14.440
It's nothing unusual

24:14.520 --> 24:16.240
yet she made a big deal out of it.

24:16.320 --> 24:17.320
Why can't she save her brother

24:17.400 --> 24:18.400
from embarrassment?

24:18.480 --> 24:20.800
That's right, Father. That's right.

24:20.880 --> 24:24.080
She's so busy with the wedding banquet

24:24.160 --> 24:25.560
which seems to make her quick to flare up.

24:25.640 --> 24:26.880
???She...                            ???Servant.

24:31.400 --> 24:33.080
Get me the ruler.

24:35.720 --> 24:38.120
Father! I was wrong!

24:38.200 --> 24:39.560
I won't do it again, Father.

24:39.640 --> 24:41.680
???Yes. He knows...      ???Father, I was wrong!

24:44.120 --> 24:45.480
Why are you still here?

24:45.560 --> 24:46.960
Do I have to get it myself?

24:47.720 --> 24:48.720
Yes, Sir.

24:48.800 --> 24:50.320
Father, I was wrong!

24:50.400 --> 24:52.200
Father, I was wrong!

24:52.280 --> 24:53.600
I won't do it again, Father.

24:53.680 --> 24:56.480
I won't do it again. Spare me the beating!

24:56.560 --> 24:58.360
I was wrong, Father!

25:08.680 --> 25:09.680
Let's go.

25:13.280 --> 25:15.440
Father, I was wrong!

25:15.520 --> 25:18.120
Father! Stop!

25:18.200 --> 25:20.560
Father, I was wrong!

25:22.480 --> 25:23.800
Father...

25:36.240 --> 25:37.640
Guard Nanfeng, you are in a hurry.

25:37.720 --> 25:38.720
Where are you going?

25:38.800 --> 25:39.800
I'm dealing with something

25:39.880 --> 25:40.880
on behalf of Mistress.

25:45.640 --> 25:47.160
Is it the much-talked-of matter

25:47.240 --> 25:48.880
related to the son of Butler Hua?

25:49.240 --> 25:50.240
Yes.

25:50.320 --> 25:53.280
Did you send him to prison?

25:53.360 --> 25:56.080
No. I just sent him back to Hua Residence

25:56.160 --> 25:57.520
and Butler Hua would decide what to do to him.

25:58.600 --> 25:59.720
Well, I see.

26:00.440 --> 26:02.680
Get back to work. I shan't hold you up.

26:17.640 --> 26:19.440
Mistress, Nanfeng is back.

26:19.520 --> 26:20.520
He brought back four young ladies

26:20.600 --> 26:21.600
from Hua Residence.

26:21.680 --> 26:23.040
They are now in the courtyard outside.

26:24.520 --> 26:26.000
People believe

26:26.080 --> 26:27.920
that wives should listen to their husbands.

26:28.640 --> 26:29.920
Not many women have the courage

26:30.000 --> 26:31.320
to stand up to that stigma.

26:32.960 --> 26:35.600
Give some money to each of them

26:35.680 --> 26:37.280
and help them prepare to leave.

26:38.120 --> 26:39.120
Yes, Mistress.

27:04.240 --> 27:05.640
The peach blossoms in the backyard bloomed.

27:05.720 --> 27:07.520
Do you want to go there to relax your mind?

27:11.320 --> 27:12.640
It's nice to go out for a walk.

28:04.320 --> 28:05.480
I have picked so many.

28:05.560 --> 28:07.200
They're more than enough to make wine

28:07.280 --> 28:08.280
and peach blossom cakes.

28:08.360 --> 28:09.360
Let's go back.

28:10.040 --> 28:11.040
I'm sorry.

28:18.160 --> 28:19.400
You don't need to apologise, Master.

28:20.320 --> 28:22.920
I know Her Highness' order

28:23.000 --> 28:24.320
has nothing to do with you.

28:26.200 --> 28:28.320
Maybe I have misled Hua Qian.

28:28.720 --> 28:31.360
Don't worry. I won't make you a concubine.

28:32.320 --> 28:35.440
But I still can't divorce her yet.

28:36.120 --> 28:37.680
If you're not agreeable, you can refuse

28:38.080 --> 28:40.160
and I'll ask my mistress to rescind her order.

28:40.800 --> 28:42.840
I know you're kind.

28:44.600 --> 28:45.680
But...

28:50.640 --> 28:51.640
this is what I want.

29:26.640 --> 29:28.520
It seems that some people are already here.

29:29.480 --> 29:30.520
Mistress.

29:32.600 --> 29:34.920
It's all right. Let's go back.

29:42.680 --> 29:44.920
Hua Rongzhou, have you grown taller?

29:45.480 --> 29:47.640
You were about the same height as me

29:47.720 --> 29:49.400
when you joined last year

29:49.480 --> 29:50.920
but now, it seems you're a little taller than me.

29:51.480 --> 29:53.640
Guard Hua is still growing.

29:53.720 --> 29:56.000
I think he's going to be a lot taller.

29:59.160 --> 30:02.680
But his face still looks like a boy.

30:03.400 --> 30:05.480
Look at him. He's so thin

30:05.560 --> 30:07.160
but his face is as round as a baby's

30:07.240 --> 30:09.000
which makes him look even younger.

30:09.080 --> 30:10.080
It is true that a round face

30:10.160 --> 30:11.920
will make people look young.

30:12.000 --> 30:17.680
I have to say those chubby cheeks are adorable.

30:17.760 --> 30:19.640
I can't help but want to pinch those cheeks

30:19.720 --> 30:20.960
and take a nibble.

30:26.400 --> 30:28.680
Relax. I'm not going to start nibbling on you.

31:13.200 --> 31:14.200
???This way, please.         ???Congratulations.

31:14.280 --> 31:16.160
???Please come in.           ???Congratulations.

31:16.240 --> 31:18.440
???Thank you...               ???Please come in.

31:18.520 --> 31:20.160
???You may put these here.      ???Here you are.

31:20.240 --> 31:21.440
???Congratulations...               ???This way.

31:21.520 --> 31:22.800
This way, please.

31:22.880 --> 31:24.360
Shopkeeper Liu.

31:25.200 --> 31:26.360
???Congratulations.              ???Thank you...

31:27.360 --> 31:28.520
Mistress, congratulations.

31:28.600 --> 31:30.520
Thank you. Please come in.

31:31.800 --> 31:33.200
Look at her.

31:33.360 --> 31:34.360
She's organised a wedding banquet

31:34.440 --> 31:35.440
for a concubine.

31:35.520 --> 31:36.520
I really don't understand her.

31:36.600 --> 31:37.640
What else could it be?

31:37.720 --> 31:39.360
???To show her generosity!         ???Thank you.

31:39.440 --> 31:41.080
It's the first time I've seen someone do so much

31:41.160 --> 31:42.520
when her husband is taking a concubine.

31:42.600 --> 31:43.600
That's true.

31:43.680 --> 31:44.800
She is really a "good wife".

31:46.120 --> 31:48.360
I'll tell my daughter not to pretend

31:48.440 --> 31:50.680
to be someone that she's not.

31:50.760 --> 31:51.760
Thank you.

31:52.120 --> 31:54.960
A girl brought up in a rich and powerful family

31:55.120 --> 31:57.800
always looks at the bigger picture.

31:57.880 --> 31:59.400
Think about your identity

31:59.480 --> 32:01.280
before talking behind someone's back.

32:01.360 --> 32:03.160
What do you girls from plebeian families have

32:03.240 --> 32:04.440
to compare to her?

32:04.520 --> 32:06.040
You're here too, Mrs Hua?

32:06.720 --> 32:08.480
If my memory serves me right

32:08.560 --> 32:10.400
your husband was just transferred here

32:10.480 --> 32:11.760
from a small town.

32:12.280 --> 32:14.120
Just a butler of humble birth.

32:14.200 --> 32:15.360
No wonder you would be

32:15.440 --> 32:16.640
that presumptuous and disrespectful.

32:17.280 --> 32:18.280
Mrs Hua...

32:18.360 --> 32:19.360
Your husband is in charge of the procurement

32:19.440 --> 32:20.440
for the Zhong family, right?

32:20.520 --> 32:21.800
He is still an errand boy

32:21.880 --> 32:23.320
after working for so many years.

32:23.400 --> 32:25.560
Shouldn't you ask yourselves why?

32:25.640 --> 32:27.480
You're right and I'm wrong, Mrs Hua.

32:27.560 --> 32:29.360
I will remember you.

32:29.800 --> 32:33.640
Don't let me hear any more gossip

32:33.720 --> 32:35.560
and watch yourselves.

32:36.280 --> 32:37.320
???Yes.                     ???This way, please.

32:38.320 --> 32:40.120
No matter what my daughter does

32:40.680 --> 32:42.520
she is the only daughter of the Hua family

32:42.600 --> 32:43.960
and the wife of Master Zhong.

32:44.640 --> 32:46.520
She and you lowly women

32:46.600 --> 32:48.480
are not equals.

32:48.920 --> 32:50.000
Long time no see.

32:52.200 --> 32:53.480
Let's go.

32:53.920 --> 32:54.920
???Congratulations.          ???Congratulations.

32:55.000 --> 32:56.960
???This way, please.          ???Please come in.

32:58.400 --> 32:59.400
Please.

32:59.480 --> 33:00.480
What brings you here, Mother?

33:00.560 --> 33:02.320
Look at what you did.

33:02.680 --> 33:04.840
You brought our family shame.

33:05.280 --> 33:06.600
Your brother...

33:06.680 --> 33:07.680
There are many people here.

33:07.760 --> 33:09.000
You should go in first, Mother.

33:12.360 --> 33:13.640
Your brother will come too.

33:13.720 --> 33:14.960
Keep an eye on him.

33:19.560 --> 33:20.600
Qian.

33:21.200 --> 33:22.200
Qian.

33:23.520 --> 33:24.520
Qian.

33:24.600 --> 33:28.320
Everyone present today is of high status.

33:28.400 --> 33:29.720
Behave yourself

33:29.800 --> 33:31.680
and don't cause me any more trouble.

33:31.760 --> 33:32.760
Don't worry, Qian.

33:32.840 --> 33:35.040
I know what I can and cannot do today.

33:35.120 --> 33:37.760
Does that mean that you will be good today

33:37.840 --> 33:41.720
but you still won't change in the future?

33:42.120 --> 33:43.480
No. I'm a changed man now.

33:43.880 --> 33:45.160
I am.

33:45.240 --> 33:46.640
I'm different now.

33:48.360 --> 33:49.840
Qian, I'm really a changed man now.

33:49.920 --> 33:51.040
I won't cause you trouble again.

34:01.520 --> 34:03.040
Concubine Mu, it is done.

34:04.440 --> 34:05.440
Wait.

34:13.640 --> 34:15.000
Put this on for me.

34:15.320 --> 34:16.720
This hairpin doesn't seem to go well

34:16.800 --> 34:18.240
with your outfit today...

34:18.320 --> 34:20.600
It's all right. Just put this on for me.

34:21.440 --> 34:22.520
Yes, Concubine Mu.

34:44.240 --> 34:45.800
There will be a wide range of pastries

34:45.880 --> 34:47.360
and melon seeds here. Help yourself...

34:47.440 --> 34:48.600
Be careful.

34:49.120 --> 34:50.440
Help yourself to them.

34:50.520 --> 34:52.240
???Congratulations, Mistress.       ???Mistress.

35:06.560 --> 35:07.680
Lord is here. Lord.

35:08.840 --> 35:09.840
Lord.

35:11.360 --> 35:12.360
Have a few more drinks.

35:12.440 --> 35:13.480
Come on...

35:14.280 --> 35:15.480
Let me fill it up for you.

35:15.560 --> 35:16.880
???You can't leave.            ???Of course not.

35:18.240 --> 35:19.760
Come here and sit with me.

35:20.320 --> 35:21.320
Lord.

35:21.480 --> 35:23.720
???Let's sit here.      ???Why are you so happy?

35:25.120 --> 35:27.240
Lord, all the guests have arrived.

35:27.320 --> 35:28.680
Let me lead you to your seat.

35:28.760 --> 35:30.480
The wedding will start soon.

35:30.560 --> 35:32.680
You're not surprised by my attendance?

35:32.760 --> 35:34.520
I was surprised just now.

35:40.440 --> 35:41.720
You haven't answered me yet.

35:42.360 --> 35:44.560
Why are you so happy?

35:44.640 --> 35:46.840
Lord, that's a good question.

35:47.280 --> 35:49.680
Actually, I am not happy

35:49.760 --> 35:52.200
but it is a happy occasion after all

35:52.280 --> 35:54.440
so I'd better put on a smile.

36:01.480 --> 36:02.520
Hua Qian

36:02.600 --> 36:04.920
are you completely indifferent to my senior now?

36:07.520 --> 36:08.680
How could it be?

36:09.200 --> 36:10.400
You're overthinking, Lord.

37:00.560 --> 37:01.640
There is no need

37:01.720 --> 37:03.680
to do away with the tea-serving ceremony.

37:04.080 --> 37:05.840
I don't need to have tea served to me.

37:07.840 --> 37:09.200
You're making Mu Yao break the rules

37:09.280 --> 37:11.200
that are passed down from the ancestors.

37:15.320 --> 37:16.800
I only suggested this with the best intentions.

37:16.880 --> 37:17.960
Since you're not agreeable

37:18.040 --> 37:19.120
then keep the tea-serving ceremony.

37:19.720 --> 37:21.280
Now you don't even bother to act

37:21.360 --> 37:22.920
all demure and virtuous anymore.

37:24.640 --> 37:26.880
What, you don't like it?

37:27.200 --> 37:28.400
Then divorce me.

37:53.640 --> 37:55.920
Mu Yao, here's a bracelet.

37:56.280 --> 37:57.960
A little something from me.

38:27.200 --> 38:28.400
Come on.

38:28.480 --> 38:29.680
Come on.

38:33.160 --> 38:34.280
???Dig in.                         ???Let's eat.

38:34.360 --> 38:35.520
???Tuck in.                 ???Enjoy yourselves.

38:35.600 --> 38:37.400
???Start eating.                        ???Okay.

38:37.480 --> 38:38.520
???Come on.                        ???Let's eat.

38:39.520 --> 38:40.600
Eat as much as you want.

38:41.480 --> 38:42.640
If the food is not enough

38:42.720 --> 38:44.040
I'll get the cook to prepare more.

38:47.440 --> 38:49.640
???Come on.                      ???Let's drink.

38:58.280 --> 39:00.120
???Cheers.                           ???Come on.

39:00.200 --> 39:01.360
Please.

39:02.560 --> 39:03.960
Let's drink.

39:04.360 --> 39:06.520
A toast to you, Mrs Hua.

39:10.280 --> 39:11.880
You don't have to be that polite.

39:17.760 --> 39:18.960
Come on.

39:19.040 --> 39:20.400
A toast to you.

39:20.760 --> 39:21.920
Have more.

39:23.840 --> 39:25.000
Qianzhi.

39:25.200 --> 39:26.600
Try this. It's nice.

39:26.680 --> 39:28.680
???Mistress.              ???Where's my brother?

39:28.760 --> 39:29.960
Okay...

39:30.400 --> 39:33.360
I saw him wandering in the backyard just now.

39:34.120 --> 39:35.520
Tell him the ladies here

39:35.600 --> 39:37.000
are all from rich families

39:37.080 --> 39:38.080
and that he'd better not move around

39:38.160 --> 39:39.160
lest he offend someone.

39:39.240 --> 39:40.720
Yes, Mistress.

39:41.280 --> 39:42.400
Come on. One more drink.

39:43.120 --> 39:44.400
???Sure.                             ???Come on.

39:44.480 --> 39:45.800
Thank you all for coming today.

39:45.880 --> 39:46.880
Let's drink.

39:53.240 --> 39:54.800
Greetings, Young Master Hua.

39:59.160 --> 40:01.000
Hey, beauty.

40:02.240 --> 40:04.400
I'm Mistress's maid.

40:07.800 --> 40:10.000
Right. I remember you.

40:10.520 --> 40:13.000
Mistress instructed me to tell you

40:13.440 --> 40:14.440
that the ladies here

40:14.520 --> 40:15.520
are all from rich and powerful families.

40:15.600 --> 40:17.560
You'd better not move around

40:17.640 --> 40:18.680
so as not to offend someone.

40:18.880 --> 40:20.760
I'm full.

40:20.840 --> 40:24.040
I'll just stay here and not go anywhere.

40:24.600 --> 40:27.480
Huang went to get some hangover soup for me.

40:27.560 --> 40:29.480
After the banquet is over

40:29.560 --> 40:30.720
tell my mother that

40:30.800 --> 40:32.000
she can come here to find me.

40:32.360 --> 40:33.760
I'll take my leave.

40:33.840 --> 40:34.840
All right.

41:21.360 --> 41:22.920
Are you going to be Zhong Yelan's concubine?

41:24.200 --> 41:25.200
Yes.

41:26.120 --> 41:28.440
If this is not what you want, I can...

41:28.520 --> 41:29.520
This is what I want.

41:32.480 --> 41:33.680
You will regret this.

41:34.680 --> 41:36.360
Let's talk about it when I really regret it.

41:37.600 --> 41:38.760
Junior Lord

41:39.200 --> 41:41.920
I don't know why you keep coming to me

41:42.560 --> 41:44.760
but please don't come to me again.

41:45.200 --> 41:47.080
I will get someone to catch you

41:47.200 --> 41:48.640
every time I see you.

41:53.760 --> 41:54.880
I told you before

41:57.040 --> 41:58.280
but you forgot.

42:01.080 --> 42:02.640
What motive do you have for coming to me?

42:04.320 --> 42:05.640
I swear.

42:05.720 --> 42:07.840
I fell in love with you at first sight

42:07.920 --> 42:09.320
and can't stop thinking about you.

